user.signature:
足够坚持的人风雨再大也不怕，足够担当的人生活再难也不怕，只要你足够用心，走过才会无遗憾！只要你足够真诚，留下的才是最好的！
存善念，得善果，越努力行恶，越危险！
自觉、自重、自爱 自知之明！做一个内心阳光的人！
前方有路 ，未来可期，无论经历了什么，请记得带上你的感恩和善良，去遇见温暖和善良！

哈喽大家好。 
v❤️：Qc-1995-

{"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p1.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038","https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/ff5a70b608b04307bbb486d55324f72f~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=4010531038"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_
